<P>LOCK AND KEY: A <HI>MUSICAL ENTERTAINMENT,</HI> IN TWO ACTS, As performed at the THEATRE ROYAL, COVENT-GARDEN.</P>
<P>BY <HI>PRINCE HOARE, E&s;q.</HI> AUTHOR OF MY GRANDMOTHER&mdash;NO SONG NO SUPPER&mdash;THE PRIZE, &amp;c.</P>
<P>CORRECTLY TAKEN FROM THE PROMPT-BOOK.</P>
<P>LONDON: PRINTED FOR T. N. LONGMAN, PATERNOSTER-ROW <HI>1796. [Price One Shilling.]</HI></P>
</DIV1>
